# ChatComposer

`TxChatComposer` renders a controlled chat textarea with attachment chips, guarded send behavior, keyboard shortcuts, and customizable action rows. It is intentionally transport-agnostic: hosts own message persistence, upload state, and submit side effects.

<script setup lang="ts">
import { ref } from 'vue'

const text = ref('')
const sent = ref<string[]>([])

function onSend(payload: { text: string }) {
  sent.value.unshift(payload.text)
  text.value = ''
}
</script>

